    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine sancte Trinitatis. Anno dominice incarnacionis millesimo centesimo
                        quadragesimo nono, die octava mensis septembris, indictione duodecima, in
                            <placeName ref="#places/4179">Pomposia</placeName>. Dum esset domnus
                            <persName key="#Abbots" ref="#people/4310">Iohannes</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs> <orgName key="#Monasteries #Slave" 
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1460">Sancte Marie de Pomposia</orgName> et cum eo
                        erant domnus <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Martinus de Adriani">
                            Martinus de Adriani</name></persName> et 
                        <persName key="#Witness #Other_clerics"><name ref="Iohannes">Ioannes</name></persName> 
                        <rs key="#Other_clerics">clericus</rs> eiusdem monasterii
                        et <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Gaurellus de Saracino">Gaurellus de Saracino</name></persName> 
                        et <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Petrus">Petrus</name></persName> filius 
                        <persName><name ref="Radaldus de Goro">Rathaldi</name></persName> de <placeName ref="#places/3596">Gauro</placeName> et 
                        <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Hugolinus">Ugolinus</name></persName>
                        filius <persName key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus"><name ref="Iohannes">Iohannis</name></persName> 
                        <rs key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus">castaldionis</rs> et alius 
                        <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Hugolinus">Ugolinus</name></persName> filius 
                        <persName><name ref="Raginmundus">Raimundi</name></persName> et me
                        presente <persName key="#Tabellio"><name ref="Gisbertus">Giberto</name></persName> 
                        <rs key="#Tabellio">tabellione</rs>, interrogavit ipse domnus Iohannes abbas 
                        <persName key="#Slave"><name ref="Petrus Rufus">Petrum Rufum</name></persName> 
                        filium quondam Trucie Guidonis de Canis, si ipse esset <rs key="#Slave">famulus</rs>
                        supradicti monasterii de Pomposia aut non. Tunc ipse Petrus surexit dicens:
                        ‘Per quadraginta annos est quod ego servivi nomine servitutis et famulatus
                        in supradicto monasterio pro et in tempore septem abbatum’. Quod audiens
                        supradictus donnus Iohannes abbas rogavit me presentem Gibertum tabellionem
                        ut, ita sicut audivi de ore ipsius Petri Rufi, in presencia ipsorum testium
                        qui suprascripti sunt et sic scripsi ego, in die mensis, indictione
                        supradicta.</ab>
                </div>
